text: José María Claro Gómez (born 25 September 1970) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
